Subject: {{collective.name}} wants a Virtual Card

{{> header}}

<div class="hidden">Virtual Card Request submitted by {{user.firstName}}</div>

<h1>{{collective.name}}</h1>

<style>
  th {
    text-align: left;
  }
</style>

Dear admin of {{host.name}},

<p>
  {{user.firstName}} wants their Collective, {{collective.name}}, to receive a Virtual Card.
  Since this is still a manual process, you'll need to manually create a virtual credit card and assign it to the
  collective through <a href="https://opencollective.com/{{host.slug}}/edit/host-virtual-cards">your settings panel</a>.
</p>

<h2>Collective details</h2>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <td>{{collective.name}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Url</th>
    <td><a href="https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}">https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}</a></td>
  </tr>
  {{#if collective.website}}
  <tr>
    <th>Website</th>
    <td>{{collective.website}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if collective.twitterHandle}}
  <tr>
    <th>Twitter</th>
    <td>{{collective.twitterHandle}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/if}}
  <tr>
    <th>Description</th>
    <td>{{collective.description}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

{{#if notes}}
<h2>Message</h2>
<p>
<blockquote
  style="color: #6a737d;font-size: 14px;text-align: left;padding: 0.5em 0.75em;margin: 1em 0;border-left: 3px solid #e4e4e4;white-space: pre-line;">
  {{notes}}</blockquote>
</p>
{{/if}}

<br /><br />

{{> footer}}
